Description:Verify Badlands / Scrubland / Bayou each tap for their two basic-land-type colours (CR 305.6). The ONLY red source on the board is Badlands, so casting Lightning Bolt ({R}) forces Badlands to tap for {R}. The ONLY green source is Bayou, so casting Giant Growth ({G}) forces Bayou to tap for {G}. Scrubland's white side is exercised in the heuristic Sengir test; here it sits as an extra land.

